reviewText: In this movie you will learn about ruins,castles,churches,pubs,inns this and much much more!

I was looking for a short video about the English Countryside, and this video is it!  In spite of being made in 1992 and apparently being a promo for American Airlines, it gave a good sense of the landscape (including London) and history, and what it might be like to visit.  I will treasure this video!
